OL,3,CSon of couple detained in Iran says
OL,4,Cit's a relief to hear they are alive
OL,6,FThe family of a Sussex couple jailed
OL,7,Fin Iran say it's a relief to hear
OL,8,Fthey're alive, after speaking to them
OL,9,Fon the phone for the first time.
OL,11,FLindsay and Craig Foreman from Forest
OL,12,FRow, were arrested in January, while
OL,13,Fon a motorcycle tour around the world,
OL,14,Fand later charged with espionage,
OL,15,Fwhich they deny.
OL,17,FTheir son from Folkestone is urging
OL,18,Fthe government to do everything they
OL,19,Fcan to bring them home.
