OL,3,CSon of couple detained in Iran says
OL,4,Cit's a relief to hear they are alive
OL,6,FThe couple are now being held in
OL,7,Fseparate prisons.
OL,9,FAccording to the family, Lindsay is in
OL,10,FQarchak Prison, and her husband Craig
OL,11,Fis being held in Fashafoyeh, a prison
OL,12,Ffacility in central Tehran.
OL,14,FThe family believe the prisons are
OL,15,Finhumane, unsanitary and have little
OL,16,Faccess to clean drinking water.
OL,18,FTheir son Joe Bennett says hearing his
OL,19,Fparents' voices gives him strength.
