OL,3,CSon of couple detained in Iran says
OL,4,Cit's a relief to hear they are alive
OL,6,FHe continued to say: "To know that
OL,7,Fthey are both okay and as well as can
OL,8,Fbe, in the conditions that they are in.
OL,10,F"It gives you that strength.
OL,12,F"You've heard their voices; it makes
OL,13,Fyou want them home even more.
OL,15,F"So now we are going to kick on and do
OL,16,Fwhat we can."
OL,18,FThe family is urging the UK Foreign
OL,19,FOffice to send the funds without
OL,20,Ffurther delay.
