OL,3,CSon of couple detained in Iran says
OL,4,Cit's a relief to hear they are alive
OL,6,FThe Folkestone and Hythe said:" This
OL,7,Fis absolutely a painful and horrific
OL,8,Fsituation and I just can't imagine
OL,9,Fwhat Joe and the family are going
OL,10,Fthrough.
OL,12,F"And the urgency of getting action is
OL,13,Fabsolutely clear, everything has to be
OL,14,Fdone to get Craig and Lindsay home.
OL,16,F"It's an absolutely awful situation
OL,17,Fand cannot continue for one day more."
