OL,3,CSon of couple detained in Iran says
OL,4,Cit's a relief to hear they are alive
OL,6,FAn FCDO spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fdeeply concerned by reports that two
OL,8,FBritish nationals have been charged
OL,9,Fwith espionage in Iran.
OL,11,F"We continue to raise this case
OL,12,Fdirectly with the Iranian authorities.
OL,14,F"We are providing them with consular
OL,15,Fassistance and remain in close contact
OL,16,Fwith their family members."
